---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms of Service - Auto Download Monetized Center"
  description="Read our terms of service and understand the rules for using Auto Download Monetized Center."
>
  <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 p-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-8">
          Terms of Service
        </h1>
        
        <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
            Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
          </p>

          <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing and using Auto Download Monetized Center, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement.
          </p>

          <h2>Description of Service</h2>
          <p>
            Auto Download Monetized Center is a platform that indexes and provides links to free, open-source software and applications from official sources. We do not host any files directly but provide links to original publishers and developers.
          </p>

          <h2>Legal Software Only</h2>
          <p>
            We strictly prohibit and do not index:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Cracked, pirated, or illegally modified software</li>
            <li>Keygens, patches, or license circumvention tools</li>
            <li>Malware, viruses, or potentially harmful software</li>
            <li>Copyrighted software without proper licensing</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>User Responsibilities</h2>
          <p>Users agree to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Use the service only for lawful purposes</li>
            <li>Respect intellectual property rights</li>
            <li>Not attempt to circumvent security measures</li>
            <li>Not use automated tools to scrape or abuse the service</li>
            <li>Verify software licenses before use</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Download Links and Monetization</h2>
          <p>
            Download links may be processed through SafelinkU for monetization purposes. By clicking download links, you acknowledge:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Links may redirect through advertising services</li>
            <li>We may earn revenue from downloads</li>
            <li>Original download sources remain unchanged</li>
            <li>All software remains free and legal</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p>
            The service is provided "as is" without any warranties:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>We do not guarantee software functionality or safety</li>
            <li>Download links may become unavailable</li>
            <li>Software versions may not be the latest</li>
            <li>We are not responsible for third-party content</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            Auto Download Monetized Center shall not be liable for:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Any damages resulting from software use</li>
            <li>Data loss or system damage</li>
            <li>Unavailable or broken download links</li>
            <li>Third-party service interruptions</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All software listed remains the property of their respective owners. We respect intellectual property rights and will remove content upon valid DMCA requests.
          </p>

          <h2>Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Your privacy is important to us. Please review our <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Privacy Policy</a> to understand how we collect and use information.
          </p>

          <h2>Modifications to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the service constitutes acceptance of modified terms.
          </p>

          <h2>Termination</h2>
          <p>
            We may terminate or suspend access to our service immediately, without prior notice, for conduct that we believe violates these terms.
          </p>

          <h2>Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with applicable laws, without regard to conflict of law provisions.
          </p>

          <h2>Contact Information</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:legal@autodownloadcenter.com" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">legal@autodownloadcenter.com</a></li>
            <li>Contact Form: <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Contact Page</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>